name: Kamala Harris
email: info@timkaine.com
subject: Make no mistake, ours is a people-powered campaign. I am relying on your $10 contribution today to win this election and fight for the promise of America.
body: $10. That’s the donation I am asking you to split between my campaign and TimKaine’s campaign. I’ll explain more, but if that is all you need to hear, youcan make a donation at this link below:https://secure.actblue.com/donate/tk-2024-kamala[https://secure.actblue.com/donate/tk-2024-kamala] If you've saved yourpayment information with ActBlue Express, your donation will go throughimmediately: DONATE $10[https://secure.actblue.com/donate/tk-2024-kamala?express_lane=true&amount;=10]DONATE $50[https://secure.actblue.com/donate/tk-2024-kamala?express_lane=true&amount;=50]DONATE $100[https://secure.actblue.com/donate/tk-2024-kamala?express_lane=true&amount;=100]DONATE OTHER [https://secure.actblue.com/donate/tk-2024-kamala] In four days,Virginia will decide who they want as their next U.S. Senator and their nextPresident. Ultimately, this election is about two different visions for ournation. One focused on the future . And one focused on the past . Tim Kaineand I believe in a future where every person has the opportunity not just toget by, but to get ahead. Where no child has to grow up in poverty. Whereevery worker has the freedom to join a union. Where every person hasaffordable health care, child care, and paid leave. Where every senior canretire with dignity. But Donald Trump and his extremist Republican allies wantto take our country backward. They intend to cut Social Security and Medicare,to give tax breaks to billionaires and big corporations and to make workingfamilies foot the bill, and end the Affordable Care Act. America has triedthese failed policies before. We are not going back. Generations of Americansbefore us led the fight for freedom. Now, the baton is in our hands. Toprotect the right to vote. To get assault weapons off of our streets. Torestore reproductive freedom, reversing Donald Trump's extreme abortion bans.Tim Kaine has spent his entire career fighting to improve the lives ofeveryday Virginians, and he knows there is more to be done. If you are readyto join us in the fight for freedom and opportunity for all, please split adonation of $10 to our campaigns.
